This directory is meant to store static files that need to be processed such
as original images to convert to sprites, SCSS files that will be converted
to CSS, etc.

# To generate main CSS file:
sass --watch  components/scss/main.scss:src/eso/static/css/main.css

# To generate events_embed CSS file:
sass --watch  components/scss/events_embed.scss:src/eso/static/css/events_embed.css

# To generate CSS sprites:
bin/glue components/sprites src/eso/static/sprites --url=../sprites/ --recursive --padding=1 --namespace=
